data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2-full bath all-brick ranch home with a spacious fenced backyard. Featuring separate family and living rooms all those entertaining needs. A welcoming front porch invites you to relax and enjoy the neighborhood and outdoors. Hardwood floors throughout create a warm and classic ambiance and the newer HVAC system will keep that peace of mind. Attached garage for added convenience. This well-maintained property seamlessly combines classic charm with modern comfort. Your opportunity to own this inviting home so make it yours. Schedule your showing today!
